CD Management Tool

Role in the project

Development

COMPANY

EY (Ernst & Young)

YEAR

2023

Private project

Idea

Create a web application for the Content Delivery team, allowing them to clearly track the production process of dynamic content creation requests. Additionally, it should provide a clear overview of who is involved in the task and the quality with which it was completed. Furthermore, it should offer comprehensive tracking regarding the fulfillment of KPIs by the production team and their approval by the QA team.

Problem

The current data SharePoint-based list contains a lot of mixed and unnecessary information, making it less reliable for reading. This makes it more difficult to build personalized and modern apps using the SharePoint list as a database.

Solution

Weâ€™ll had to create a new SharePoint list and make sure the information was organized properly, and used a SharePoint API to connect the front-end application with the data on the list.

User Persona

Main functionalities:

  • All in one, app with all of the relevant applications and websites required for the daily tasks
  • Filters by portfolio regarding information and main personalities
  • KPIs tracker (so managers can follow their assigned producers efficiency and quality of work)
  • QA tracker (to know the status of the requests regarding the compliance of the production parameters)
  • Requests dashboard (to know the people involved in each request and their respective status regarding the production process)
  • Key contacts of each department
